(1502, 1502, '2022-11-04 12:16:50', '2022-11-04 12:16:50', '-Vd3VY4L-wA', 'Aquarium air pump for air assist laser engraving - is it better than vacuum cleaner?', 'Ortur Aufero 2 with LF laser module arrives with air assist nozzle. In the review video I could test it only with vacuum cleaner, but several comments suggested me to test it with aquarium air compressor. In this video I am testing ACO-318 45W air compressor from Banggood. The testing will cover laser engraving and cutting. \n\nAir pump presented in the video: https://www.banggood.com/custlink/DD3dN2MrJp\nSpring sale from 3.9 to 3.26: \nSaving Tips  https://ban.ggood.vip/11ia3\nSaver Deposit Sale  https://ban.ggood.vip/11ia4\nSpring Trendy Sale  https://ban.ggood.vip/11ia5\nYour Exclusive Benefits  https://ban.ggood.vip/11ia8\n\nOrtur Aufero 2 laser engraver review video: https://youtu.be/y_b4poZoovo\n\nList of all laser engraver related videos:\nhttps://www.mytechfun.com/videos/laser_engraving\n\nContents:\n0:00 Introduction\n1:29 Unboxing\n3:00 Airflow comparison (vacuum cleaner)\n3:38 Airflow comparison (air pump)\n4:39 Noise measuring\n5:05 Engraving (with and without air assist)\n6:19 Cutting (with and without air assist)\n7:46 Conclusions\n\n#laserengraving #aircompressor #airassist', '00:00:00', '-Vd3VY4L-wA', 'video/youtube', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/-Vd3VY4L-wA/mqdefault.jpg', '(min-width: 400px;)', 'image/jpeg', 'UCYihfm2hMVxsiDSk_o0lcow', '2022-11-02 01:14:04'),
(1503, 1503, '2022-11-04 12:16:50', '2022-11-04 12:16:50', 'wjH48V3uANE', 'DIY Laser Cutter Air-Assist & Enclosure', 'Ever since I mounted a 10W Endurance Laser onto my CR-10, I knew I needed to build an enclosure to capture and exhaust all the smoke outside. While I was at I also decided to add an air-assist to get cleaner cuts.\n\nThe Laser I\'m using is the 10W model from Endurance Lasers, the review of which you can check out here: https://youtu.be/R9OHYq-Ws-w\nEndurance Lasers Website: http://endurancelasers.com/\n\nExhaust fan on Aliexpress: http://s.click.aliexpress.com/e/cVzMfvUU\nDucting on Aliexpress: http://s.click.aliexpress.com/e/c7yVlmgY\n\nSupport me (for free) while shopping online (affiliate links):\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nAliexpress: http://s.click.aliexpress.com/e/b3a0ISl6\nGearBest: https://www.gearbest.com/?lkid=11143361\nBanggood: https://www.banggood.com/custlink/D3G3GMUOYL\nAmazon (US): https://amzn.to/2pJVveJ\nAmazon (DE): https://amzn.to/2pK1YFx\neBay.com: http://ebay.us/xd6vPa\neBay.de: http://ebay.us/AwHtLQ\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nMy links:\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nInstagram: https://instagram.com/datulabtech/\nWebsite: https://datulab.tech\nStore: https://store.datulab.tech\nThingiverse: https://www.thingiverse.com/DatulabTech\nGithub: https://github.com/datulab\nE-Mail: info@datulab.tech\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------', '00:00:00', 'wjH48V3uANE', 'video/youtube', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/wjH48V3uANE/mqdefault.jpg', '(min-width: 400px;)', 'image/jpeg', 'UCYihfm2hMVxsiDSk_o0lcow', '2022-11-02 01:14:20'),
(1504, 1504, '2022-11-04 12:16:50', '2022-11-04 12:16:50', '-JBIMSJ--v8', 'DIY Homemade Laser Cutter', 'The full documentation for my latest Laser builds can be found here:\nhttps://www.furtherfabrication.com/resources?category=Laser\r\n\nIn this video I share my process of designing and building a co2 laser cutter using a combination of \'V\' & \'T\' slotted aluminium profile 3d printed parts. I wanted a larger cutting area than my old K40 chinese laser cutter had, and I\'m a sucker for a challenge.\n\n\nFAQ:\nCost:\n Total cost of the build was around NZD$3000 (US$2k)\nElectronics:\n AWC608 DSP controller - I purchased mine from lightobject though in hindsight i\'d buy something directly out of China in the future.\nLaser Tube:\n Bought from Aliexpress, though you may have better options depending on your location.\n\n\n\nInstagram:\nhttps://www.instagram.com/further_fabrication/\n\nWebsite:\nfurtherfabrication.com\n\nMusic used:\nFREI - Moody\nLiam.M - Medicine\nLiam.M - Voyager', '00:00:00', '-JBIMSJ--v8', 'video/youtube', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/-JBIMSJ--v8/mqdefault.jpg', '(min-width: 400px;)', 'image/jpeg', 'UCYihfm2hMVxsiDSk_o0lcow', '2022-11-02 01:14:39'),
