(1506, 1506, '2022-11-04 12:16:50', '2022-11-04 12:16:50', 'QtEF6c1t2tM', 'I Built A Laser Cutter! (For Under $700!)', 'So, laser cutters are pretty cool. I\'ve Wanted one for quite a while, the only thing stopping me from getting one being the cost. A few Months ago, however, I realized that building one from scratch was less difficult than I thought, So I decided to try and build one cheaply to save some money.\n\nI spent A lot of time on this project and the video for it, so Subscribing would be greatly appreciated if you liked the video and want to support me.\n\nThank you all for watching!\n\nInkscape Link - https://inkscape.org/release/inkscape-1.2/\nLaserWeb Link (What I Use Now) - https://laserweb.yurl.ch/\nMarlaser - https://github.com/mentaldemise/MarLaser\n#lasercutting \n\nMusic:\n--------------------------------------------------------------------\nMusic from Uppbeat (free for Creators!):\nhttps://uppbeat.io/t/soundroll/good-thing\nLicense code: VVB3NEX91JYKMMR8\n--------------------------------------------------------------------\nMusic from Uppbeat (free for Creators!):\nhttps://uppbeat.io/t/barry-dallas/turn-it-up\nLicense code: JU1ST2XGWPTQVUYK\n--------------------------------------------------------------------\nMusic from Uppbeat (free for Creators!):\nhttps://uppbeat.io/t/all-good-folks/free-flowin\nLicense code: FVRUDUODGR9QKDBN\n--------------------------------------------------------------------\nMusic from Uppbeat (free for Creators!):\nhttps://uppbeat.io/t/soundroll/get-the-funk-in\nLicense code: BX9ODET4GAJAKJ01\n--------------------------------------------------------------------\nMusic from Uppbeat (free for Creators!):\nhttps://uppbeat.io/t/noise-cake/chunky-nuts\nLicense code: S6OWGAUSL8P0BQAF', '00:00:00', 'QtEF6c1t2tM', 'video/youtube', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/QtEF6c1t2tM/mqdefault.jpg', '(min-width: 400px;)', 'image/jpeg', 'UCYihfm2hMVxsiDSk_o0lcow', '2022-11-02 01:14:54');
