easy with Eloquent\n\n    Get data from linked tables (relationships) without SQL headaches. Even sub-queries are automatically created by Laravel, and all this is performance-optimized.\n\nLearn basic Laravel features playfully:\n\n        Models\n\n        Accessors / Mutators\n\n        Seeders\n\n        Fakers\n\n        Soft-Deletes\n\n        Stubs\n\n        Blade\n\n        Configuration settings\n\n\nFurthermore, you will have learned how to define and use constants in Laravel.\n\nWhat you’ll learn\n\n        Create a PHP / Laravel9 driven Backend for your Business application\n        Learn how to use the fantastic Spatie Media Library Plugin\n        Learn to use the powerful Laravel Eloquent Database engine, that makes even subqueries a breeze\n        Create a real Real Estate project\n\nAre there any course requirements or prerequisites?\n\n        Beginner to Intermediate PHP knowledge\n\nWho this course is for:\n\n        PHP developers who want to create apps faster and much better\n        IT Graduates who seek a carrier in an interesting an well paid field of work (Laravel development)\n\n#Laravel #PHP #Morioh\n\nNote: If you have any copyright issue with the content used in our channel or you find something that belongs to you, before you claim it to Youtube, SEND US A MESSAGE and the respective content will be DELETED right away. Thanks for understanding.\n\n◼️◼️◼️◼️◼️◼️◼️◼️◼️◼️◼️◼️◼️◼️\n👕 Merchandise: https://www.moteefe.com/store/developer?cp=WP6JDT\n🌎 Social Network for Developers: https://morioh.com/', '00:00:00', 'Pi_K6B7MxeM', 'video/youtube', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Pi_K6B7MxeM/mqdefault.jpg', '(min-width: 400px;)', 'image/jpeg', 'UCYihfm2hMVxsiDSk_o0lcow', '2022-11-11 10:49:00'),
